‚óèThe Old Fashion Man
Most of men paid attention to the impression of simple yet elegant. They were more concerned with their own judgments than others. And, they didn't like to dress something excessive or too flashy.
‚óèToday Fashion Man
Most of men now pay attention to style and their personality suitability in dress. They follow current trends, they wear simple and elegant impression, and they like to dress something flashy.

So, if we look at the earlier times their fashion was more concerned with impression of elegance and casual. But today, the fashion is very fashionable. And, fashion will always develop from time to time.
